N.Y. Comp. Codes R. & Regs. Tit. 9 ยง 4815.8 - Issuance by commission

State Regulations

When the commission has determined that the applicant
possesses the requisite qualifications to receive a license, the commission
shall issue a license as a bingo supplier upon payment by the applicant of a
license fee to be determined in accordance with the schedule contained in the

Bingo Control Law. Notes
